trans-unit.source: Represents the binding element used to specify the queuing communication properties for a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service that uses the native MSMQ protocol.
trans-unit.target: Representerer bindingselementet brukes til å angi køegenskaper for kommunikasjon for en [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenester som bruker den opprinnelige MSMQ-protokollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement> enables the user to set the properties of the queued communication channel.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement>lar brukeren til å angi egenskapene i kø kommunikasjonskanalen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: The queued communication channel uses MSMQ for its transport.
trans-unit.target: I kø kommunikasjonskanalen bruker MSMQ for transporten.

trans-unit.source: This binding element is the default binding element used by the MSMQ standard binding (<xref:System.ServiceModel.NetMsmqBinding>).
trans-unit.target: Denne bindingselementet er standard Bindingselement som brukes i MSMQ standard bindingen (<xref:System.ServiceModel.NetMsmqBinding>).</xref:System.ServiceModel.NetMsmqBinding>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Applies the settings of this configuration element to the specified <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement> binding element.
trans-unit.target: Gjelder innstillingene for dette konfigurasjonselementet for den angitte <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>Bindingselement.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement> to which settings are applied.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>til hvilke innstillinger brukes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>

trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Type>objektet som representerer bindingstypen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an integer that specifies the maximum size of the pool that contains internal MSMQ message objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et heltall som angir den maksimale størrelsen på gruppen som inneholder interne MSMQ meldingsobjekter.

trans-unit.source: The internal MSMQ message object pool is used to avoid allocations of these objects when sending and receiving messages.
trans-unit.target: Intern MSMQ meldingen objektutvalget brukes til å unngå tildelinger av disse objektene ved sending og mottak av meldinger.

trans-unit.source: The maximum pool size is a performance tuning parameter.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er en ytelse justering parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 8.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 8.

trans-unit.source: An integer that specifies the maximum size of the pool that contains internal MSMQ message objects.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir den maksimale størrelsen på gruppen som inneholder interne MSMQ meldingsobjekter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an enumeration value that indicates the queued communication channel transport that this binding uses.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en opplistingsverdi som angir i kø kommunikasjon kanal transport som bruker denne bindingen.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ does not support Active Directory addressing when using SOAP Reliable Messaging Protocol, so do not set <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.QueueTransferProtocol%2A> to <xref:System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol> when <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.UseActiveDirectory%2A> is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Støtter ikke MSMQ Active Directory adressering ved bruk av SOAP pålitelig meldingstjeneste protokollen slik stiller ikke <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.QueueTransferProtocol%2A>til <xref:System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol>når <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.UseActiveDirectory%2A>er satt til `true`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.UseActiveDirectory%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol> </xref:System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.QueueTransferProtocol%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol"></xref> enumeration value that indicates the transport used for message delivery between queue managers.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ServiceModel.QueueTransferProtocol"> </xref> nummereringsverdi som angir transport brukes for meldingslevering mellom køen administratorer.

trans-unit.source: Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether queue addresses should be converted using Active Directory.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en boolsk verdi som angir om køen adresser skal konverteres ved hjelp av Active Directory.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ queue addresses can consist of path names or direct format names.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ-kø-adresser kan bestå av banenavn eller direkte formatnavn.

trans-unit.source: With a direct format name, MSMQ resolves the queue name using DNS, NetBIOS, or IP.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ løser kønavn med DNS-, NetBIOS- eller IP-med et direkte formatnavn.

trans-unit.source: With a path name, MSMQ resolves the queue name using Active Directory.
trans-unit.target: Med et banenavn løser MSMQ kønavn ved hjelp av Active Directory.

trans-unit.source: By default, the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] queued transport converts the URI of a message queue to a direct format name.
trans-unit.target: Som standard i [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] i kø transport konverterer URIEN for en meldingskøen til et direkte formatnavn.

trans-unit.source: By setting the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.UseActiveDirectory%2A> property to `true`, an application can specify that the queued transport should resolve the computer name using Active Directory rather than DNS, NetBIOS, or IP.
trans-unit.target: Ved å angi den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.UseActiveDirectory%2A>egenskapen `true`, et program kan angi at i kø transport bør løse datamaskinnavnet ved hjelp av Active Directory-i stedet for DNS-, NetBIOS- eller IP-.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement.UseActiveDirectory%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if queue addresses should be converted using Active Directory; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis køen adresser som skal konverteres med Active Directory. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
